article_metadata.Title: US top court sidesteps major ruling on Obamacare contraception coverage

og.description: The U.S. Supreme Court Monday ducked a major ruling on a challenge by Christian nonprofit employers to an Obamacare mandate to provide female workers health insurance covering birth control by sending the cases back to lower courts for further proceedings.
